{"tid":924633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【太過份】竹籤插新巴座椅底 女乘客刮傷小腿","createTime":"2018-12-02T08:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T11:06:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9f643a12b231ceb5f43400fcb158c1643805c4","tid":924633,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"一輛新巴904線，駛經旺角亞皆老街期間，上層一名女乘客向車長求助，指座位插着一支竹籤，刮傷她的小腿流血。車長得悉後停車報警，由救護員將傷者送院。<br />\n警員到場調查，插有竹籤的座位在上層右邊第三行走廊位。竹籤長約10厘米，插在座墊與凳架之間，露出一端。當62歲的女事主坐下之際，右腳小腿被刮傷。警員調查後認為案件無可疑，列作意外受傷處理，<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181202/large/1543734786_7606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181202%2Flarge%2F1543734786_7606.jpg&h=730d4c76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181202/large/1543734392_c1f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181202%2Flarge%2F1543734392_c1f5.jpg&h=01bb2835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181202/large/1543734392_09d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181202%2Flarge%2F1543734392_09d9.jpg&h=8a69ee2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181202/58983200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58983200&d=Qx2xuUP7W70gsE4E%2BeShXQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=549af669\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181202%2F58983200&h=88b22f6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181202/58983200</a>"},{"pid":"93c8a5f7b71c66dbbf19f6379ffdb0483523be44","tid":924633,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cit